author: Kuokka77
description:
A collection of STU's YM work. Two have been previously featured in my channel, but only in emulated form (and "stereo").

Tracklist:

00:00 Bombtro 
03:26 Chiprape
07:02 Electrox
10:01 Fuck Machine
12:12 Ready to Score
14:44 ST-God Back from Hell

Art in order of appearance:

Frost - "Älgaråsgabber" (1st at Grep 2006 pixel gfx compo)
Lobo - "Cobretti in Wonderland" (2nd at Mountainbytes 2023 combined gfx compo)
Critikill - "Cheesy Future" (2nd at Silly Venture 2023 SE Atari ST/E gfx compo)
Lycan - "Drink" (3rd at Revision 2013 oldskool gfx compo)
Slayer - "School of Oldskull" (2nd at Revision 2011 oldskool gfx compo)
Jade - "Don't Shit On My Grave!" (2nd at Deadline 2022 oldschool gfx compo)

French CA4003290 Atari STe with new Mean Well RPD-60A PSU (SidecarTridge.com variety). Playback using SND Player v1.51. Brainworx VST effects applied.

title: Atari music: STU times six (STe🎧bx_)
